The evidence with the title 'Estimated impact of the American Recovery And Reinvestment Act ... ' says Feb 20, 2015  ... In calendar year 2014 , ARRA— which was enacted in 2009— raised real gdp by between a small fraction of a percent and 0.2 percent and increased the number of full - time - equivalent jobs bybetween ... CBO now estimates that the total impact over the 2009 – 2019 period will amount to nearly $ 840 billion . 
